    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "In the case where the off state doesn't have a value (i.e. means don't use the attribute in the search) the count should be the number of hits for 'don't use' rather than the number of hits for 'false'   I'd like someone from the project to validate that before I go changing the tests to match my assumption.\n",
