    "body": "@vvo @rogerroelofs I'm actually working with @rogerroelofs on this issue.\n\nAs the PR stands, this is exactly how I want it to behave in my case. I see the value of the `disabled` suggestion, but feel like that should be a different option (`autoHideContainer` is pretty explicit, and aligns with other core widgets).\n\nCould be `disableOnEmpty` or something.\n",
